data.title: DJ Muggs – Grown Up Rap
data.text:
Been looking forward to this for a while; the teaming up of Raz Fresco with one of hip-hop’s greatest producers.

More from the upcoming, DJ Muggs produced The Eternal Now album by Raz Fresco, which is now confirmed as being set for release on July 26.

Second single from The Eternal Now album by Raz Fresco and DJ Muggs, coming very soon.

After hyping it up on the socials, Raz Fresco finally drops the first taste of his upcoming album with DJ Muggs.

Latest video from Mooch and DJ Muggs, and their recent album from March, Roc Star.

More visuals from DJ Muggs and Mooch, and the new project, Roc Star.

Full release of the new project from DJ Muggs and the latest generation of street emcees, this one a collaboration with Mooch.

Second drop from the upcoming DJ Muggs and Mooch album out next month, which we now know it called Roc Star.

UPDATE: There’s also now a video. Check it below:

After dropping the latest instalment of the Soul Assassins series last year, DJ Muggs is returning to his run of albums with underground hip-hop’s best artists. He and Mooch have an album dropping in March, including this first track.
